messages.content: What are the acknowledgements for comfyui-colornodes?

The project makes use of code from the following repositories:

- Color node from [comfy_mtb](https://github.com/melMass/comfy_mtb/) by [melMass](https://github.com/melMass/)
- Image Remove Color node from [WAS Node Suite](https://github.com/WASasquatch/was-node-suite-comfyui/) by [WAS](https://github.com/WASasquatch)

Both repositories are licensed under the MIT License.
